@Node "output" "The Output Gadget"

It's here the date is showed, in this version it will always be started
with the following date: 1st Hammer, 1367 DR, Midnight.

@EndNode

@Node "quit" "The Quit Gadget"

This gadget is used to quit the program.

@EndNode

@Node "cal" "The Change Calendra Gadget"

In the Forgotten Realms Campaign there are more than one calendra system,
this gadget is used to choose the calendra system which you want to use in
your campaign. At the moment you can choose all those from the 2nd ed campaign
box, but not the Dragon Year, for there isn't enough information about the
system, even those at TSR don't know more what they have printed in the box.
 
@EndNode

@Node "time" "The Time Type Gadget"

You can choose to change the year, month, day, hour or minute, the two
following gadgets are used to change it one step forward or backwards.

@EndNode

@Node "minus1" "The Backward Gadget"

This gadget is used to change the time backwards one step, how much depends
on the mood you have choosen.

@EndNode

@Node "plus1" "The Forward Gadget"

This gadget is used to change the time forward one step, how much depends
on the mood you have choosen.

@EndNode

@Node "year" "The Year Gadget"

This is used to set the year more faster than useing the Time Type Gadget,
this can be set to move the time in step of 10, 100 or 1000 year. 

@EndNode

@Node "minus2" "The Year Backward Gadget"

This gadget will remove the number of years set on 'The year Gadget'.

@EndNode

@Node "plus2" "The Year Forward Gadget"

This gadget will add the number of years set on 'The year Gadget'.

@EndNode

